---
title: Calorie Smart Korean-Style BBQ Turkey with Smashed Cucumber Salad and Ginger Rice
description: Turkey gets the classic Korean BBQ treatment with this recipe! Umami-packed turkey pairs beautifully with some quick-charred bok choy and a delightfully fresh and flavourful smashed cucumber salad to satiate those Korean grill house desires!

